+    /**
+     * Fast check if both operands are "small values" in financial scenarios.
+     * For values where |x| < 10^9 and |y| < 10^9, the product |x*y| < 10^18,
+     * which is guaranteed to fit in a long without overflow check overhead.
+     * This optimization targets financial trading where values typically
+     * have ≤10 digits of precision.
